  "section_name": "Financial Analysis",
  "text": "Bank of America demonstrated revenue growth acceleration in Q3 2025, with total revenue reaching $48,221,000,000, representing a 3.33% year-over-year increase from the prior period. This marks a meaningful recovery from Q2 2025, which saw a -0.69% YoY decline on revenue of $46,666,000,000. The sequential improvement from Q1 2025 revenue of $46,989,000,000 suggests stabilizing top-line performance heading into the fourth quarter.",
